Output docs/journal.gif
Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 908
Set Height 490
Set Padding 12
Set Framerate 15
Hide
Type "~/loom/docs/journal_driver.sh jg >/dev/null 2>&1 & tmux kill-session -t jg 2>/dev/null; tmux new-session -d -s jg -x 100 -y 28 ~/loom/bin/journal; tmux set -t jg status off; tmux setw -t jg window-size manual; clear; tmux attach -t jg"
Enter
Sleep 1
Show
Sleep 20
Hide
Sleep 1
